### üß† Advanced Example: Auto Responder Bot

A simple auto-responder bot example:

```php
namespace App\Listeners;

use Khody2012\LaravelBale\Events\MessageReceived;
use Khody2012\LaravelBale\Facades\Bale;

class AutoResponder
{
    public function handle(MessageReceived $event)
    {
        $chatId = $event->message['chat']['id'];
        $text = trim(strtolower($event->message['text'] ?? ''));

        $responses = [
            'hi' => 'Hello! üëã',
            'how are you' => 'I‚Äôm doing great, thanks for asking!',
            'bye' => 'Goodbye! See you soon üëã',
        ];

        $reply = $responses[$text] ?? "I didn‚Äôt quite catch that. Type 'help' for available commands.";

        Bale::sendMessage($chatId, $reply);
    }
}
```

